<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Da nhan su kien de xet duyet</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #0f0f0f; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #e5e5e5; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #1a1a1a; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #2a2a2a; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #facc15 0%, #f59e0b 100%); padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #000; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; }
    .body { padding: 36px 40px; }
    .body p { line-height: 1.7; color: #d4d4d4; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .info-box { background: #111; border: 1px solid #3f3f46; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 6px 0; }
    .info-label { color: #71717a; font-size: 13px; }
    .info-value { color: #e5e5e5; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
    .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; background: #fef9c3; color: #854d0e; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a; }
    .footer p { margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #525252; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🏢 HighShow</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Xin chao <strong>{{organizerName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Chung toi da nhan su kien cua ban va dang tien hanh xem xet. Ket qua se duoc thong bao trong <strong>{{slaText}}</strong>.</p>
      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Ten su kien</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{eventName}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Trang thai</span>
          <span class="info-value"><span class="badge">Dang cho duyet</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>Trong thoi gian cho ket qua, ban co the:</p>
      <ul style="color:#d4d4d4; font-size:15px; line-height:1.8; padding-left:20px;">
        <li>Kiem tra lai thong tin su kien tren Dashboard</li>
        <li>Lien he ho tro neu can gap: <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color:#facc15;">{{supportEmail}}</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>Tran trong,<br/><strong>Doi ngu HighShow</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© {{year}} HighShow. Khong reply email nay — day la email tu dong.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
